Name: Soukaku
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Soukaku's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

There's a folder that appears to be dedicated to documenting food... But does hardtack really belong in here?
